{"word":"G4406 - πρώϊμος - prṓïmos - pro'-ee-mos - Early","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρώϊμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prṓïmos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro'-ee-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Early</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முன்மாரி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"early rain, autumn rain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4404 - πρωΐ - prōḯ - pro-ee'/4404\">G4404</a>; <i>dawning</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>autumnal</i> (showering, the first of the rainy season): - early.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}